Man known only as Jason uploaded the video to YouTube . 
  He used a needle, a pair of pliers and his sister in law to pop a grape-sized cyst on his wrist . 
  His wife filmed the process and he cried out in pain as she hammered the needle into the swelling . 
  GP Dr Arun Ghosh has condemned the method of popping a cyst with a needle and a screwdriver . 
  The man from Vancouver said the cyst was a ' ganglion'